{"tid":1137573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓總：高雄發大財","createTime":"2019-05-04T01:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T21:53:24.000Z","uid":34409,"like":248,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"f43ce2ee439d07e5875253b063a51f95950c75b8","tid":1137573,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:45:39.000Z","msg":"以下是黃捷質詢韓國瑜內容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：黃議員，這沒有矛盾啊，因為似乎你所關注的焦點，一直在大陸&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n議員：<span style=\"color: red;\">那具體上要什麼嘛？</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：當然是高雄要什麼！<br />\n<br />\n議員：要什麼啊？<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：<span style=\"color: blue;\">高雄要發財呀！對不對？</span><br />\n<br />\n議員：天啊！市長，我們都要發財，<span style=\"color: red;\">但具體上你要開放什麼東西、什麼項目，<br />\n或者說現在有什麼限制，你要現在告訴我啊！</span>我們想知道的是這個，<br />\n<br />\n不是說高雄要發財這麼簡單就可以呼嚨過去<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：<span style=\"color: blue;\">黃議員，總目標是高雄要發財</span><br />\n<br />\n議員：這個都是我們共同的目標<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：很多事情，我們所做的一切事情都是希望往高雄發大財這個目標<br />\n<br />\n議員：<span style=\"color: red;\">那具體上你要做什麼嘛！</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜：這個自經區是其中之一，好不好？謝謝<br />\n<br />\n議員：市長&hellip;&hellip;你真的懂自經區嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜最後似乎有點不屑黃捷為何一直苦苦追問<br />\n<br />\n彷彿認為發大財這句話就能說明一切<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=aFEX2b4J1mQ&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaFEX2b4J1mQ%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9zk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=0d2f6356\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=aFEX2b4J1mQ&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"bf7f7248789968b81341fd6711801cb5c791623a","tid":1137573,"uid":35790,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:46:33.000Z","msg":"原來係草包一個"},{"pid":"b62187f4cc2edfb6509827ce6713378c584d1c56","tid":1137573,"uid":23170,"like":123,"dislike":0,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:03:20.000Z","msg":"原來係發大財，我仲以為要征服宇宙"},{"pid":"38fece1f37a0a524c4676f150515ceca11549cf3","tid":1137573,"uid":63843,"like":45,"dislike":0,